metadata.name: from the peripheries of luminous vision ⊹ 01
metadata.description:
───°࿐  
bathing in a diamond spray of the sky  
breathing in light, exhaling shade  
something of you remains here

tingling through layers, it retains its power  
almost to resurface with edges, almost to sight  
phantasmic presences - upright and serene

there none speaks of any ‘mine’ and ‘thine’  
rather porous embrace of shimmers  
dwelling in the tinctures of alchemical minds  
hue of quested substance pulsates the divine

in the rhythms of sweet dissonance  
intuitively swaying our cores in blissful joy  
the neural nodes reverberate softly  
in their serendipitous finds

───°࿐  
Collection part of Poetic.AI  
(2022, MP4, 2048 x 2048 px, 60 FPS)
